Title: GECF reports 12% surge in global LNG shipments in Jul. 2025
Description: Global liquefied natural gas (LNG) exports reached 36.55 million tonnes (Mt) in July 2025, marking a 12% year-on-year increase and setting a record high for the month, according to the Gas Exporting Countries Forum (GECF).
